27\. Truly did God fulfil  
The vision for His Apostle:  
Ye shall enter the Sacred  
Mosque, if God wills,  
With minds secure, heads shaved,  
Hair cut short, and without fear.  
For He knew what ye  
Knew not, and He granted,  
Besides this, a speedy victory.

